data.description:
This BREATHTAKING custom built home on 6.4 acres features 3 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, an upstairs bonus room, high ceilings through out, a safe room, and so much more! Home was built in 2010. The kitchen showcases custom maple cabinets and granite countertops, 36" gas range, built in microwave, and walk-in pantry with decorative door. The living room has high ceilings with unique, custom made beams and fireplace that goes the full 14’ feet. The master bedroom is gorgeous with a walk-in tile shower and elegant soaking/jetted tub. The laundry room has a fun retro floor and a decorative door just like the pantry door. Approximately 3300 sq ft heated. 
Outside you find a porch and brick fireplace for enjoying the views along with covered areas; great for parties. The property is 6.4 acres, fully fenced with a 2 stall barn, tack/feed room, and a HUGE shop that fits atvs, trailers, livestock supplies, cars, whatever your heart desires.  A must see for anyone in the market! Call Sarah 903-343-2669 for a showing! For sale by owner.
